@baseUrl = http://localhost:8081

### Save draft email (simple)
POST {{baseUrl}}/save-draft-email?toEmail=fake@test.test&subject=Draft%20email%20test&body=Hello%20World

### Save draft email with attachments
POST {{baseUrl}}/save-draft-email
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="toEmail"

fake@test.test
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="subject"

Draft email test with attachments
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="body"

Hello World with attachments
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="attachments"; filename="intellicare_solutions.jpeg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ../../main/resources/images/intellicare_solutions.jpeg
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="attachments"; filename="xyz_bookstore.webp"
Content-Type: image/webp

< ../../main/resources/images/xyz_bookstore.webp
--WebAppBoundary--

### Read inbox - last 10 emails
GET {{baseUrl}}/read-inbox?maxEmails=10

### Read inbox - unread only
GET {{baseUrl}}/read-inbox?unreadOnly=true&maxEmails=10

### Read inbox - filter by subject
GET {{baseUrl}}/read-inbox?subjectFilter=Flashback%20Sunday!&maxEmails=20

### Read inbox - filter by sender
GET {{baseUrl}}/read-inbox?fromFilter=no-reply@accounts.google.com&maxEmails=20

### Read inbox - combined filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/read-inbox?subjectFilter=TEST%20Alpha&unreadOnly=true&maxEmails=5

### Read inbox - filter by recipient (to) (replace with actual email address)
#GET {{baseUrl}}/read-inbox?toFilter=<your-actual-email@gmail.com>&maxEmails=20&dateAfter=2026-02-13

### Read inbox - filter by body text
GET {{baseUrl}}/read-inbox?bodyFilter=Economic&maxEmails=20

### Read inbox - filter by date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/read-inbox?dateAfter=2026-02-13&dateBefore=2026-02-16&maxEmails=20

### Read inbox - filter by date after
GET {{baseUrl}}/read-inbox?dateAfter=2025-09-12&maxEmails=10

### Read inbox - complex combined filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/read-inbox?fromFilter=googleplay-noreply@google.com&dateAfter=2026-01-01&unreadOnly=false&maxEmails=15

